{"tid":912573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大 對生存愈無感覺","createTime":"2018-11-22T18:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T12:53:11.000Z","uid":205419,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f5377f7a78d31d3ac75a81614bef73ac3e7a7d","tid":912573,"uid":205419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"從小時候 探索新事物<br />\n感到好奇 有興趣<br />\n即使望着渺小的螞蟻 亦能感到快樂<br />\n正因為小時候容易尋找快樂<br />\n往往都會沉醉於快樂之中<br />\n也容易開始幻想 自我中心<br />\n害怕失去 <br />\n害怕沒有機會再享受快樂及未來<br />\n單純的以為快樂就是人生<br />\n隨著成長<br />\n經歷愈多<br />\n見識人間醜惡<br />\n朋友背叛 脆弱的愛情 故人離去 世間種種百態<br />\n也開始對身邊事物厭倦 <br />\n看破紅塵 看穿人心世事 甚至討厭<br />\n難以再得到快樂<br />\n了解到生存於世界也只不過是如此<br />\n只不過是去感受<br />\n快樂經歷完 傷痛也經歷完<br />\n剩下的只是繼續觀看 經歷更多<br />\n反正再痛的都痛過<br />\n便開始無畏死亡<br />\n死亡也只不過是種解脫<br />\n也只不過是人海中少了一粒沙"},{"pid":"b0e25de7e1e0fecb2de521ddd3e7afece6e4f026","tid":912573,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦"},{"pid":"0d74c22f63e60f692765b8449740390f084b461c","tid":912573,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"等咩"},{"pid":"ad3cdb70533331ae6a130d23f4dd81720c025dea","tid":912573,"uid":166827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38859d2fef1c27d63e3a329d7512f958394f35cd","tid":912573,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"u again"},{"pid":"c9be13a29ff5a19bae7d47c3e815845f4bed48a3","tid":912573,"uid":205419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3cdb70533331ae6a130d23f4dd81720c025dea","tid":912573,"uid":166827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"唔係歌黎"},{"pid":"d7241d086ff85388066d